data.name: LabelAbout.Text
data.value: SteamPulse is a free and open source software that accesses the information of various games on Steam using the SteamAPI and can guide gamers when purchasing games by key. Steam Pulse is the result of a year of effort by the CodeMage team. during this time we received positive feedback from users and fixed the reported problems, we hope that now we have been able to provide SteamPulse with a perfect experience.
